Start project with Spring boot, then go to Chrome or browser and hit the below URL
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html#/

3 API's
1. saveDepartmentEmployee -- Saves Department and Employees associated with that
2. getEmployeeByDept  --- Pas Department ID get EmployeeNames associated with that
3. getDeptByEmp  -- Give Empid as input and it will Return Department Name

Sample Request for Save :

[
  {
    "departmentId": 1,
    "departmentName": "HR",
    "description": "HR DePT",
    "employeeDetails": [
      {
        "address": "ADRESS 1 2 3",
        "employeeId": 1,
        "employeeName": "ABC234",
        "phoneNumber": "2354646"
      },
{
        "address": "ADDRESS 456",
        "employeeId": 2,
        "employeeName": "ABC123",
        "phoneNumber": "2514548748"
      }
    ]
  }
]




